<br>
Did a group with two mages and two necros along with a shaman in PoD the other night and we were taking down the level 60 Misquitos without much problem.  Greatest experience I've gotten so far, 1 blue of regular 60 exp in about 25 min.  Parchments dropped like mad as well.<br>
<br>
When forming together a pet group, we all know that Mages are ideal, but Necromancer's are no pushovers (they can snare/root too, good crowd control).<br>
<br>
